------------System Requirements--------------------
1. Read user input
2. Read a file with string
3. find and replace the words with ADJECTIVE, NOUN, VERB, ADVERB
----------------------------------------------------
--------MODULES----------------------------------
re module - used to find the words and replace.
-------------------------------------------------

-------PSEUDO---------------------------------------
1. START
2. TRY opening file
    DISPLAY 'file not found' if not found
3. READ contents
4. DISPLAY contents
5. READ input
6. REPLACE ADJECTIVE with input
7.READ input
8. REPLACE NOUN with input
9. READ input
10. REPLACE ADVERB with input
11. DISPLAY updated contents
12.OPEN file
13.OVERRITE the file with contents

---------------------------------------------------------------------